fm: int find_minimum(int a[], int n) { 	int c, min, index; 	 	min = a[0]; 	index = 0; 	 	for (c = 1; c < n; c++) { 		if (a[c] < min) { 			index = c; 			min = a[c]; 		} 	} 	 	return index; }
long linear_search1(long a[], long n, long find) { 	long c; 	 	for (c = 0 ;c < n ; c++ ) { 		if (a[c] == find) 			return c; 	} 	 	return -1; }
long linear_search2(long *pointer, long n, long find){ 	long c; 	 	for (c = 0; c < n; c++) { 		if (*(pointer+c) == find) 		return c; 	} 	 	return -1; }

void reverse_array(int *pointer, int n){ 	int *s, c, d; 	 	s = (int*)malloc(sizeof(int)*n); 	 	if( s == NULL ) 		exit(EXIT_FAILURE); 	d = 0 ; 	for ( c = n - 1; c >= 0 ; c-- ){ 		*(s+d) = *(pointer+c); 		d++; 	} 	 	for ( c = 0 ; c < n ; c++ ) 		*(pointer+c) = *(s+c); 	 	free(s); }

void concatenate(char p[], char q[]) { 	int c, d; 	c = 0; 	 	while (p[c] != '\0') { 		c++;  	 	} 	 	d = 0; 	 	while (q[d] != '\0') { 		p[c] = q[d]; 		d++; 		c++;	 	} 	 	p[c] = '\0'; }

void merge(int a[], int m, int b[], int n, int sorted[]) { 	int i, j, k; 	 	j = 0; 	k = 0; 	 	for (i = 0; i < m + n;i++) { 		if (j < m && k < n) { 			if (a[j] < b[k]) { 				sorted[i] = a[j]; 				j++; 			}else { 				sorted[i] = b[k]; 				k++; 			} 			i++; 		}else if (j == m) { 			for (; i < m + n;) { 				sorted[i] = b[k]; 				k++; 				i++; 			} 		}else { 			for (; i < m + n;) { 				sorted[i] = a[j]; 				j++; 				i++; 			} 		} 	} }
int string_length1(char *pointer){ 	int c = 0; 	 	while( *(pointer + c) != '\0' ) 		c++; 	 	return c; }
void reverse2(char *x, int begin, int end){ 	char c; 	 	if (begin >= end) 		return; 	 	c          = *(x+begin); 	*(x+begin) = *(x+end); 	*(x+end)   = c; 	 	reverse2(x, ++begin, --end); }
void copy_string(char *target, char *source){ 	while(*source){ 		*target = *source; 		source++; 		target++; 	} 	*target = '\0'; }
int check_vowel(char a){ 	if ( a >= 'A' && a <= 'Z' ) 		a = a + 'a' - 'A'; 	 	if ( a == 'a' || a == 'e' || a == 'i' || a == 'o' || a == 'u') 		return 1; 	 	return 0; }
